						<msItem rend="visible" class="lccn.loc.gov/sh85070287">
							<locus from="2r" to="22r"/>
							<title xml:lang="he-Latn-x-lc">Tiḳun soferim </title>
							<title n="0" xml:lang="he">תקון סופרים</title>
							<note>
								<p>A tract based on a decision found in Devar Shemuel of Samuel ben Abraham Aboab. On folio 3v is a haskamah of Jacob Aboab, then follow two teshuvot by Moses Zacuto. Folio 17 contains haskamot from the rabbis of Venice yeshivah, with voting results provided on folio 18r. Folio 18v begins a teshuvah of Isaac Pacifico.</p>
							</note>
							<author>
								<persName key="http://viaf.org/viaf/97604990" xml:lang="en">Aboab, Samuel ben Abraham, -1694</persName>
								<persName xml:lang="he" key="http://viaf.org/viaf/97604990">אבוהב, שמואל בן אברהם</persName>
							</author>
						</msItem>
						<msItem rend="">
							<locus from="22v" to="27r"/>
							<title xml:lang="he-Latn-x-lc">Binyan ne῾arim</title>
							<title xml:lang="he">בנין נערים</title>
							<author>
								<persName xml:lang="en">Jacob Bellilos</persName>
								<persName xml:lang="he">בליליוס, יעקב</persName>
							</author>
							<note>
								<p>A refutation of the preceding work, dated 1734.</p>
							</note>
						</msItem>
						<msItem rend="">
